ade for more xp.<br><br>So though it may be new to some its very true this tactic has been around for a long while.<br><br><br>Faad <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6666cc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/upiousitydebiers.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Piousity DeBiers</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#ffff00>(12/17/01 9:07:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fstormofdragonsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=174.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hey Aggy</span><hr size=1> Well now that all my RL excitement is over and running to the hospital daily I should be on a bit more again. AoE when I got to do it --exp was much faster, I like the concept when someone other then enchanters have to work in the grp-- to me it is such a waste of a wizard to have em in a grp and they are there for snare or evac--hell get a druid for that--lets use wizards for the massive damage spells--I have tried to learn every class(minus bard) so I know how to grp with them--I will still grp with aggy anywhere anytime-- later<br><br><br>Pious <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6666cc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/usmark.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Smark</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#ffff00>(12/18/01 7:25:39 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fstormofdragonsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=174.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> AoE spells and PvP</span><hr size=1> I don't know why you all are complaining... I played on Rallos Zek for awhile.  You can't use AoE at all without wiping out your group too.  Now try that on for size.  After reading Verant's full response, I think they balanced the zone fine.  Come on 40+ mobs at a time IS cheater.  Their first reaction was a bit harsh granted, but born of good intentions. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6666cc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/usleezstakk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sleezstakk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 78<br> <font color=#ffff00>(12/18/01 5:15:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fstormofdragonsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=174.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: AoE spells and PvP</span><hr size=1> That's really interesting Smark. You actually DON'T know why I'm complaining. Perhaps if you had read the top of this thread as well as the bottom, then maybe you would.<br><br>I am complaining because another stooge who does everything an uberclown tells him has declared how AoEs are useless. Which they clearly are not.<br><br>Aggy <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/usleezstakk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sleezstakk</A> at: 12/18/01 5:27:57 pm<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/fstormofdragonsfrm5.showMessage?topicID=187.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/fstormofdragonsfrm5.showMessage?topicID=186.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fstormofdragonsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=174.topic&index=9><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fstormofdragonsfrm5.threadControl?topicID=174.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt